calls.requestDetails: Open a new trade from inventory items. Offered items for trades will not be available for use in the inventory.

calls.name: PublishDraftItem
calls.summary: Initiates a publish of an item from the working catalog to the public catalog.
calls.requestDetails: The call kicks off a workflow to publish the item to the public catalog. The Publish Status API should be used to monitor the publish job.

calls.name: PublishUgcItem
calls.summary: Initiates a publish of a item from the working catalog to the public catalog.
calls.requestDetails: The call kicks off a workflow to publish the item to the public catalog. The Publish Status API should be used to monitor the publish job.

calls.summary: Refresh Subscriptions.

calls.summary: Submit a report for a review
calls.requestDetails: Submit a report for an inappropriate review, allowing the submitting user to specify their concern.

calls.summary: Submit a report for an item, indicating in what way the item is inappropriate.
